Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the patient doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has yet to regain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess would be that it's heat stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat stroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I collapsed, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made sure to stay hydrated and get plenty of sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he keep making that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked so hard so that everyone could have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who do you think I am?{RAWR RAWR FIGHT DA POWAH}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:05.43,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(670,849)\pos(816,504)}#10 Shorthand\NShorthand Original
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I do is lose my trump card and I'm reduced to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan has destroyed Oriana's Shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing? You feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there are no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that "All-Direction Rational Formation," then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already all set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming you know how to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things going on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, Oriana's counterspell went off in the middle of one of the events.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A single student collapsed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to slip away during the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kamijou Touma go berserk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave the rest to you, since you know the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't move now, that student will have collapsed for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be why we lament our own inexperience?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is an unexpected twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed the location of Oriana Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's near Futsuka Station in the Seventh District.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, she's at Futsuka Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Futsuka Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already passed that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's headed north.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The road up ahead splits into three separate paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just took one. Keep going, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found her!{that sure is some leisurely running - nah we're not in a hurry}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!{you'd assume the bus would wait for two students in Academy City}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kami-yan, was there anyone else besides Oriana on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no driver, either!{oic}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 514457.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rune that Stiyl placed on it back at the maintenance yard was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to take more than that to get me warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I panicked, it seems my underwear's gotten all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt someone who has nothing to do with this when you cast that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she look like she was involved in this at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone{\i0} is involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one were to wish for it, it would be quite easy to become a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really wasn't my intention to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. You weren't the one I was trying to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of weird kids hanging around Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Tsuchimikado?!{I'll shout at you without nullifying him first!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just canceled the fire attribute, the symbol of regeneration and healing, with blue letters.{再生と回復の象徴である火属性を青の文字で打ち消しただけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it's a spell which disables you if you're already hurt enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't dispel it without destroying the card?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to save him, you'll have to get to me as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder how much more he can take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like time is against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what that Stab Sword is worth to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's going to change history or alter the world in some grand way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hurting people just to get your hands on it is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does nothing more than cause meaningless violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I will destroy it with this hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say I'm just doing my job, but that would be rude to my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The methods to be employed for this trade have been left in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't just go around playing with people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she hits me with that spell from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Shadow Swords. {it had a bloody 'S'!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get bored of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't she using the same attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like using the same attack over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just foreplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she said that she wouldn't use the same spell twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's got so many combinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Blade Crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move from that spot, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die if I move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares about something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the effort Fukiyose put into making the Daihaseisai a success is being rendered meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll just sit idly and let you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't good enough for Kamijou Touma!{WHO THE HELL DO YOU THINK I AM}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His right hand is that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop Rest!{official unless "resuto" means sth in another language}{I've always wondered how hard he's gotta hit to 1 hit ko pretty much anyone}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!{Boobs! I mean, Tsuchimikado!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Tsuchimikado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a violent boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what you did; the button fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're not bad for an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm accustomed to dealing with counterattacks, so you just make me want more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave that with you for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that our little game is over just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be turning up the heat from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What about Tsuchimikado—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect only lasts 20 minutes. It'll go away on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little worrywart esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now destroy Stab Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be a piece of cake for you with your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right for me to just destroy it though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Academy City were attacked because of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, she'll be the one to take the fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's smack-dab in the middle of enemy territory for magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll calm down and come up with a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll confer with my superiors to see what we should do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into a little trouble, but I made it here just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{TS: What things have happened?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got their hands on the billboard so they probably already know about Stab Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't affect the trade itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that anyone {\i1}can{\i0} get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially if this trade will make everybody happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The original Stab Sword does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the people invented the legend about it on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what is written here true? Charles Conder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We at the British Museum hadn't noticed it at all until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what might you be holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the tales have snowballed onto each other over the years, we can't be completely sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is called the "Croce di Pietro" in its original country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Translated, however, it is "the tool that was used to crucify Peter."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St. Peter's cross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that the point of their trade is fundamentally changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this trade happens, it will be the end of Academy City as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it could be even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's something dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Croce di Pietro"—something like "The Cross of St. Peter."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The founding location of the main base of the Roman Catholic Church, the Vatican,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the large patch of land where St. Peter was buried, on which they put a cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can also say the opposite.{what}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere the "Croce di Pietro" is erected will become the dominion of the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it'll make everything go as planned for the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will recall the change, and they'll just think it's business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how unfair the request, or how heavy the burden,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be a world where everyone will feel only happiness.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Academy City is taken into the body of the Roman Catholic Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this world in which science and magic are at equilibrium,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will tilt towards the side of the Roman Catholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this trade about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably trading the rights to rule Academy City as well as the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop the trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, the world will have to face a reality even more terrible than mere destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world where everyone can only be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.84,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma! Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there's no way Index would wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you look me in the eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, what's with your outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just thinking about something naughty, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your normal clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left them with Komoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm meeting with Mom and Dad to have lunch soon, so just hold out until—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed into this so I could cheer you on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then you ran off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my best so that I could spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was I supposed to do when you ran off on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I thought you were just angry because you were hungry—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.87,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mad because you won't pay attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, getting mad over hunger is totally not Sister-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.24,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.50,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your usual biting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't have to do it if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, {\i1}you've{\i0} always been the one biting {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the real pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's been hours since we last saw Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you saw the number of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might take a while to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! So we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. From this morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you so much for your help this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I was able to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they? Friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the parents of that boy you're interested in, Mikoto-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you, we're the Kamijou family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Show them your appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you eaten lunch already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to eat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a really nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm not used to these large crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't paying much attention, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. What is this, Touya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to stare; it's just that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like father, like son...{This explains so much...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:19:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She showed us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Misaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. {HERE WE GO, TSUN TIME}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell don't I ever get any search hits from you?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just going with the flow of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if there's any sort of flow with {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, who is this girl who follows you around everywhere and where the hell does she live?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with you when we went to the ocean, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You w-went to the ocean together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who's the brown hair over there and where does {\i1}she{\i0} live?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Touma's girlfriend or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to cheer for Touma's school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I remember seeing you during the Pole Assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we eat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Kamijou Touma-kun, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Misaka's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Misaka Misuzu, Mikoto's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:28.05,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By solving the hidden puzzles, we're drawing closer to understanding their goal one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happens to Himegami when we run into her by accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Stab Sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, this epic will begin!
